<div style="background-color:#2A313F;color:#FFFFFF;padding:40px;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:2:63"><h1 style="text-align: center;">Kernersville Food Pantry Program</h1>

<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:18px;">No one should have to choose between paying bills and putting food on the table. Our food pantry&nbsp;helps bridge the gap for families and&nbsp;individuals facing food insecurity.</span>
</p></div>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:3:45"></div>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:4:25"></div>
