<img width="70" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/d3332bd7-1830-4d92-9d7c-497ca03083bf_download.png" alt="placeholder" class="img-fluid d-block my-3 mx-auto" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;" loading="lazy" / data-zesty-id="content:images:6:29">
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:13:29"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:7:97">LOCATION</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:8:21">130 E. Mountain Street</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:9:86">Kernersville, NC 27284</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:81">
					Please note clients may begin lining up before&nbsp;distribution time. The car line is located beside the Kernersville Police Department.
				</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:11:61">
					<a href="https://goo.gl/maps/kYb1B7adovRFTAJ8A"><span class="btn btn-solid btn-red">DIRECTIONS</span></a>
				</p>
				</div>
<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:22:12-1:2 Columns - Equal:1">
<img width="70" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/5921579e-95ce-4dbc-8db5-5e5c2c91b25c_clock.png" alt="placeholder" class="img-fluid d-block my-3 mx-auto" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;" loading="lazy" / data-zesty-id="content:images:14:98">
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:21:97"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:15:57">HOURS OF OPERATION</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:16:10">Mondays, Tuesdays, and Thursdays</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:17:13">11:30 am&nbsp;- 12:15 pm</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:18:80">
					Distribution will end when supplies run out each day.
				</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:19:37">
